# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [v0.0.6]

### Added

- New Wishlist button on product pages
- New wishlist page in 'my-account' page
- New wishlist section in admin pages

### Fixed

- [v0.0.5-1](https://github.com/MILG0IR/MILG0IR-Store-Design-Features/blob/main/known-issues.md) Complianz logo and others are slightly off on the admin side panel.

## [v0.0.5]

### Added

- Custom stamp card block to display the stamps/value potential for each order.
- Basic rest api to get the stamps/value potential for each order.
- Basic language functionality.
- Added plugin page links.
- Added my-account page nav block.

### Fixed

- The plugins update functionality has now been repaired and is fully functinal.

### Changed

- additions, changes and removals are now on this page, not in the code in an attempt to make the source less cluttered.

### Delayed Changed

- [DELAYED] Attempts to create the plugin in a namespace/class hierarchy.

## [v0.0.4a]

### Changed

- Repairs to the logo in the admin sidebar covering the whole page.

## [v0.0.4]

### Added

- Stamp Card account menu item and page.
- Wishlist account menu item and page.
- New admin menu pages and options.

### Changed

- Changed the admin page to allow for new options.

## [v0.0.3]

### Changed

- Minor bug fixes and changes.

## [v0.0.2]

### Changed

- Minor bug fixes and changes.

## [v0.0.1]

### Added

- Admin menu item and page.
- Custom taxonomy 'Collection'.
